# Creador Foundation

**Type:** Non-profit / foundation  
**Country:** Malaysia  
**Registration:** PPAB-01/2017 (referenced in copyright notice)  
**Copyright notice:** "Hak Cipta Terpelihara © 2025 The Creador Foundation PPAB-01/2017"

## Role

Creador Foundation is the organisation that created and operates [[schola]], a free digital career guidance platform for Malaysian secondary school students.

## Known Products / Initiatives

- **[[schola]]** — Free digital career guidance platform (launched 12 August 2024)
- **"Jom Jelajah Masa Depan Bersama Schola"** — School engagement programme
- **FIF** — Referenced alongside Schola in the school programme introduction segment (full name not stated in source)

## Core Belief

> "Everyone has talent and potential, but not everyone has the same access to opportunities."

The foundation's approach centres on democratising career awareness and opportunity access for Malaysian youth.

